Available exclusively through HBR.org: Ebook + Video Case Study!  The "HBR Guide to Persuasive Presentations" Ebook is filled with useful tips and examples from communication expert Nancy Duarte, who'll help you make each presentation a compelling pitch for your ideas. The Guide includes a 20-minute video case study featuring author  Nancy Duarte  walking you through tips covered in the Guide and is available to download (as an mp4 file) or to stream online. Duarte uses a former client, Alta Devices, to clearly illustrate how you can apply the techniques discussed in her book. Get it now for only $39.95—this Ebook + Video Case Study is available only at  hbr.org/books/Duarte .